	e available! Our Walks ‘n’ Wags certified instructors offer a day of fun a
	nd learning. Classes are intended for pet care professionals\\\, dog and c
	at owners\\\, rescue workers\\\, first responders\\\, groomers and shelter
	 workers. Course completion offers continuing education credits for PSI\\\
	, IAABC\\\, IACP and CBCC-KA members. This class has received the Animal W
	ellness Magazine Stamp of Approval and a Modern Dog Fave Find. We work wit
	h live animals in class.\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/pet-first-a
